{"tid":391053,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人既老母係生物學家？","createTime":"2017-09-07T13:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T13:30:57.000Z","uid":22719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5650d42fa2fc7825150f524fb74d234ee800ea2d","tid":391053,"uid":22719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:26:44.000Z","msg":"食完飯係都叫你食生果，話生果係唔會飽架 食啦食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3a6805a33e4cbb1c37285b32a0cb01f67af411","tid":391053,"uid":24181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:27:48.000Z","msg":"老母話生果飯前食先健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1a035b94cce75fed07c974ea596226d35fad50","tid":391053,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:28:56.000Z","msg":"飲湯唔會飽"},{"pid":"5b20c57e2e1b29cf6000e46a7460662255ea5d02","tid":391053,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:30:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf72ae01af3c657634c9ca797012e313083ac743","tid":391053,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:30:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27b107ef59fa2ae6a2f4068c4575f6d2477f30d1","tid":391053,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:30:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老母話生果飯前食先健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飯前吃較易吸收養分　飯後助消化<br />\n飯前吃水果，水果的維生素C及礦物質較容易吸收，但飯前空腹吃水果，不要選吃寒性水果，像是小番茄，避免拉肚子，另太酸的水果也不宜，像是奇異果及鳳梨等，以免傷胃；飯前吃水果，由於水果跟飯雖醣分的形式不同，但也都屬於碳水化合物豐富的食物，所以飯前水果分量若攝取較多，建議可減少一些飯量的攝取，避免攝取過多熱量造成肥胖。"}]}